Tesla in early 2013 was on the verge of bankruptcy . 
  Beset by technical problems on its flagship Model S . 
  Musk proposed that Google buy Tesla for $6 billion and promise an additional $5 billion in factory expansions . 
  In March 2013, Musk contacted Google co-founder Larry Page . 
  Tesla's fortunes changed suddenly in May 2013 when the company reported its first profit . 
 